Package: python-h2
Architecture: all
Depends: python-hpack, python-hyperframe, python:any (>= 2.7.5-5~)
Description: h2 a pure-Python implementation of a HTTP/2 protocol stack.
 It's written from the ground up to be embeddable in whatever program you
 choose to use, ensuring that you can speak HTTP/2 regardless of your
 programming paradigm.
 .
 This package installs h2 support for Python 2.

